comments: Laurie is super awesome. I had her for benefits every wed for the 1st 7 weeks from 6-9. The timeframe sucked, but she made it worth going to. Very effective teacher, doesn\'t tell you when quizzes are, but lets you know what you should know for them. She\'s so awesome that she let me complete a part of an exam I had forgotten to do after class.
Definitely knows what she is talking about, extremely helpful with questions and tests are open book/notes
Absolutely wonderful professor, one of the best I\'ve had here. Very interesting to listen to, informative, engaging, fair grader, all around good professor. I would definitely recommend taking her!
